message: UN MILLÓN DE FIRMAS Un millón de personas han firmado una petición donde exigen despedir a Amber Heard de 'Aquaman 2' después de que gracias a su acusación, se destruyera la carrera de Johnny Depp y quedará fuera de Animales Fantásticos. Ámber Head ganó la batalla final. Johnny Depp fue obligado a abandonar la saga ‘Animales fantásticos’ tras perder el juicio con ‘The Sun’ luego de llamarle "maltratador" aunque Depp presentó bastantes pruebas de maltrato por parte de ella hacia él, entre ellas fotos en el hospital y audios donde ella era la malvada de la historia. Muchos aseguran que perdió el juicio y ahora es señalado en redes sociales sólo por ser hombre. Si eres team Depp y quieres firmar la petición: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2?utm_content=cl_sharecopy_14451136_en-US%3Av3&recruiter=838572211&recruited_by_id=136d32f0-d56b-11e7-8008-b16ff1045718&utm_source=share_petition&utm_medium=copylink&utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message

message: เมื่อสัปดาห์ที่แล้วมีข่าวที่น่าตกใจสำหรับแฟนคลับภาพยนตร์ Fantastic Beasts เป็นอย่างมาก เมื่อทาง Warner Bros. ได้สั่งปลดป๋า Johnny Depp ออกจากบท เกลเลิร์ต กรินเดลวัลด์ เนื่องจากเขาแพ้การฟ้องร้องคดีความกับสื่อ The Sun เกี่ยวกับการพาดหัวข่าวว่าเขาเป็น "พวกตบตีภรรยา" เรื่องนี้สร้างความไม่พอใจให้เหล่าแฟนคลับและคนที่สนับสนุนป๋า Johnny เป็นอย่างมากค่ะ จึงทำให้ในตอนนี้เกิดการเรียกร้องให้ทาง Warner Bros. ถอด Amber Heard อดีตภรรยาของป๋าออกจากบทควีนเมรา ในภาพยนตร์ Aquaman 2 บ้าง เพราะเธอก็มีข่าวฉาวและมีหลักฐานว่าทำร้ายสามีไม่ต่างกัน ซึ่งผู้คนพากันเรียกร้องให้ถอด Amber ออกจากบทเมราผ่านทางเว็บไซต์ Change.org โดยขณะที่กำลังเขียนข่าวนี้อยู่มีคนเข้ามาลงชื่อมากกว่า 1,127,000 คนแล้ว จากที่เมื่อวานตัวเลขอยู่ที่ 980,000 คน ในขณะเดียวกัน ทางด้าน Amber ได้ออกมายืนยันว่าตนจะกลับมาเล่นบทบาทนี้อย่างแน่นอน ซึ่งยังไม่มีการคอนเฟิร์มจาก Warner Bros. แต่อย่างใด เรียบเรียงโดย #เหมียวนานะ ที่มา: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

message: [Các bạn vui lòng đọc hết status rất dài này] Hơn 700k chữ ký đòi hủy vai của CĐML Amber trong Aquaman 2. Mình đã ký rồi, các bạn ký chưa? Đòi lại công bằng cho chú nào!!!! LINK KÝ TÊN: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2?fbclid=IwAR1c0JGruYadnho4n3fiZtWghJLOSU1hdCrxDgKj7EisZuf83ryekWqlvPU *Lưu ý cần đổi IP sang 1.1.1.1 hoặc tải add-on Hola cho trình duyệt nhé các bác ui. Không là không vô được nha* Kính gửi đến cô Amber có tên cún cơm là CĐML. Nếu như ông trời quá bận nên vẫn chưa có cơ hội tặng cô một quả báo thì bọn tôi đành phải phụ ngài ấy một tay vậy ^^~ cô nghĩ việc hại chú của bọn này ra nông nổi đó mà vẫn có thể sống yên với vai diễn nạn nhân sao. Có cc ấy! ==================== Có nhiều bạn không hiểu chuyện gì thì xin copy lại bài của bạn Le Minh Chi - Group Maybe You Never Watched This Movie. Hơn 700.000 chữ ký yêu cầu sa thải Amber Heard khỏi phim Aquaman 2 sau khi Johnny Depp bị Warner Bros. yêu cầu rời Fantastic Beasts (các fan hy vọng sẽ sớm được 1 triệu) Hôm thứ Sáu tuần rồi (6 tháng 11), Depp đăng bài trên Instagram cho biết rằng Warner Bros. đã yêu cầu anh ta rời khỏi loạt phim Fantastic Beasts ngay sau khi nam diễn viên thua vụ kiện phỉ báng với báo The Sun. Vụ việc khiến các fan của Depp phẫn nộ và triển khai chiến dịch thu thập chữ ký yêu cầu Warner Bros. cũng phải chấm dứt hợp đồng với Amber Heard (vai công chúa thủy tề Mera), vào lúc này số chữ ký đã là hơn 500.000. Một số người hâm mộ cáo buộc Warner Bros. có biểu hiện "tiêu chuẩn kép" khi cho phép Heard tiếp tục đóng vai Mera trong Aquaman 2 và Justice League của Zack Snyder nhưng lại sa thải Depp khỏi vai Gellert Grindelwald. Nam diễn viên trước đó đã tố cáo vợ cũ bạo lực gia đình và đưa ra nhiều bằng chứng thuyết phục, chứng minh Amber Heard đã đánh mình và ngoại tình với nhiều người đàn ông khác nhau. Những ý kiến phản đối WB đã tràn ngập Twitter: "Tôi rất bối rối. Tôi vừa được biết Warner Bros sẽ sa thải Johnny Depp cho Fantastic Beasts. Nhưng Amber Heard đã được xác nhận sẽ trở lại trong Justice League của Snyder. Tôi cảm thấy như nếu Warner Bros định sa thải Depp, thì họ cũng cần sa thải Heard." - một người dùng Twitter viết. "Warner Bros yêu cầu Johnny Depp bỏ vai là hành vi thật đáng khinh bỉ và đáng xấu hổ. Họ đặt đặt lợi nhuận lên trên những nguyên tắc đạo đức." - một cư dân mạng khác đã tweet. "Đừng chỉ tẩy chay Fantastic Beasts vì Johnny Depp, hãy tẩy chay bất kỳ bộ phim nào của Warner Bros trong tương lai nếu nó có mặt Amber Heard trong dàn cast. Cho họ thấy chúng ta không chỉ muốn công lý cho Johnny Depp mà còn muốn họ làm điều gì đó với cô ta. Bởi Aquaman 2 sắp ra mắt và cô tavẫn chưa bị sa thải." - một fan khác khẳng định. P/s: Về phần cá nhân Ad, vẫn sẽ xem và ủng hộ Justice League Snydercut (vì đợi quá lâu rồi), nhưng sẽ không ra rạp xem bất kỳ phim nào có Amber Heard nữa, kể cả Aquaman 2. Việc người hâm mộ kêu gọi 1 triệu chữ ký không có nghĩa là WB phải làm theo, nhưng nó thể hiện cho hãng phim thấy là các khách hàng bỏ tiền ra xem phim của họ đang tức giận tới mức nào và doanh thu các phim trong tương lai của WB sẽ ảnh hưởng vì điều này.
name: Thuyền Nhỏ Lênh Đênh

message: [Đã có hơn 200.000 chữ ký vào kiến nghị đề nghị bỏ Amber Heard ra khỏi phim ‘Aquaman 2’] Bản kiến nghị được khởi động trên trang Change.org đề nghị bỏ Amber Heard ra khỏi phim do những cáo buộc bạo lực gia đình mà Amber Heard đã gây ra cho chồng cũ Johnny Depp. Theo đó, phần đầu nội dung kiến nghị ghi rằng: "Johnny Depp đã đã phơi bày Amber Heard là kẻ bạo lực gia đình Trong vụ kiện tổn thất 50 triệu USD của mình, Johnny Depp mô tả nhiều vụ bạo lực gia đình mà anh đã chịu đựng khi còn ở cùng người vợ (lúc đó) là Amber Heard, trong đó có một vụ cô ta đấm vào mặt anh hai lần và một vụ khác khiến cô ta dùng chai vodka đập vào ngón tay anh, khiến phải chịu phẫu thuật để nối lại vết thịt ngón tay. Johnny sẽ phải chịu vết sẹo này đến hết đời ", bản kiến nghị được gửi tới Courtney Simmons, SVP thuộc bộ phận Công chúng & Truyền thông cho DC Warner và DC Entertainment và Paul McGuire, SVP thuộc bộ phận Truyền thông toàn cầu tại Warner Bros." Bản kiến nghị cũng đưa những thông tin tin tức khác xoay quanh như trong quá khứ, vào 2009, Amber Heard từng bị bắt giữ do bạo lực gia đình vời người cô hẹn hò Tasya Van Ree. Vào 31/1 vừa rồi, trang DailyMail cũng công bố đoạn ghi âm trò chuyện mà cô xác nhận rằng mình đã đánh Johnny Depp: - "Em xin lỗi vì đã không...uh...uh...đánh thẳng vào mặt anh bằng một cái tát đúng cách, nhưng đó là em chỉ đánh anh chứ không phải đấm. Anh yêu à, anh không hề bị em đấm. Em không rõ chuyển động của tay mình lúc đó như thế nào, nhưng giờ anh vẫn ổn mà, em không hề làm anh đau, không hề đấm anh, em đã đánh anh thôi." Và vào 2/5, một đoạn ghi âm khác lại được công bố, đoạn ghi âm dài 31 phút, nội dung sơ lược rằng Johnny xin Amber hãy rút đơn tố cáo ra toà và hãy giải quyết một cách riêng tư, êm đềm, nhưng Amber không đồng ý vì cô cho rằng bị tổn thương danh tiếng vị bị gọi là kẻ nói dối, kẻ đào mỏ. Cũng trong đoạn thoại, Johnny đã nhắc đến tai nạn ngón tay ở trên và bị ném đồ vào giữa mặt, cũng như Amber đã nói về vụ Johnny ném điện thoại vào mặt cô. Tiếp câu chuyện Johnny đã hỏi cô có tin mình là kẻ bạo hành hay không, Amber đã nói không và nói thêm rằng: " Anh có biết là tôi nặng 52kg không, dù giờ không phải. Tôi đã nặng 52kg và gần 52kg còn anh thì to xác....Tôi có đủ mạnh để khiến anh ngã không? Tôi đủ sức khiến anh mất thăng bằng không? Anh sẽ đứng trước tòa và nói “Cô ta đã bắt đầu mọi thứ” ư? Tôi không bao giờ có đủ sức để áp đảo anh và đó là sự khác biệt giữa tôi và anh. Và đó là sự khác biệt, cả thế giới, cả toà và bồi thẩm đoàn sẽ thấy sự khác biệt lớn giữa tôi và anh.” Vụ kiện của cả hai đã bị trì hoãn đến tháng 8/2020 thay vì diễn ra tháng 2 như lịch đã định. Còn Aquaman 2 sẽ ấn định khởi chiếu vào 16.12.2022 Link bản kiến nghị: change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2 ____________________________ #PhimSắpChiếu #Aquaman2 #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard

message: Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 Amber Heard has been exposed as a domestic abuser by Johnny Depp. In his $50 million lawsuit, Johnny Depp describes many incidents of domestic abuse that he suffered at the hands of his (then) wife Amber Heard, including one incident where she punched him twice in the face and another where she shattered his finger with a vodka bottle, and his finger had to be surgically reattached. He will bear the scar from that for the rest of his life. Also, Amber Heard was arrested in 2009 for abusing a former domestic partner, Tasya Van Ree, demonstrating a repeated pattern of abuse by Amber Heard. Since Heard's divorce from Johnny Depp, she has systematically crusaded to ruin Depp in Hollywood, repeating multiple accounts of fake incidents in which she had actually abused Johnny Depp, but lied and created false accounts of him being the abuser. About the incident during which she shattered the bones in Johnny Depp's finger and nearly severed it, causing Depp to require surgery to reattach and repair it, Heard presented a false story claiming that he cut off his finger himself, dipped it in paint and scrawled obscenities all over the walls. Likewise, Heard recounts fabricated incidents of Johnny Depp hitting her in the face when she had, in fact, punched him. Though staff and neighbors in the building where she lived reported seeing no marks on her face in the hours and days after she says Johnny Depp hit her, yet she appeared in court six (6) days later with bruises on her face, asking for a temporary restraining order, which was granted. Photos of Heard from the very next day show her full face, without makeup, and not a single bruise. As Amber Heard is a known and proven domestic abuser, Warner Brothers and DC Entertainment should and must remove Heard from their Aquaman 2 film project. They must not ignore the suffering of Heard's victims, and must not glamorize a domestic abuser. Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry. Do the right thing. Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2.
name: The Anti Feminist Bank

message: Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 Amber Heard has been exposed as a domestic abuser by Johnny Depp. In his $50 million lawsuit, Johnny Depp describes many incidents of domestic abuse that he suffered at the hands of his (then) wife Amber Heard, including one incident where she punched him twice in the face and another where she shattered his finger with a vodka bottle, and his finger had to be surgically reattached. He will bear the scar from that for the rest of his life. Also, Amber Heard was arrested in 2009 for abusing a former domestic partner, Tasya Van Ree, demonstrating a repeated pattern of abuse by Amber Heard. Since Heard's divorce from Johnny Depp, she has systematically crusaded to ruin Depp in Hollywood, repeating multiple accounts of fake incidents in which she had actually abused Johnny Depp, but lied and created false accounts of him being the abuser. About the incident during which she shattered the bones in Johnny Depp's finger and nearly severed it, causing Depp to require surgery to reattach and repair it, Heard presented a false story claiming that he cut off his finger himself, dipped it in paint and scrawled obscenities all over the walls. Likewise, Heard recounts fabricated incidents of Johnny Depp hitting her in the face when she had, in fact, punched him. Though staff and neighbors in the building where she lived reported seeing no marks on her face in the hours and days after she says Johnny Depp hit her, yet she appeared in court six (6) days later with bruises on her face, asking for a temporary restraining order, which was granted. Photos of Heard from the very next day show her full face, without makeup, and not a single bruise. As Amber Heard is a known and proven domestic abuser, Warner Brothers and DC Entertainment should and must remove Heard from their Aquaman 2 film project. They must not ignore the suffering of Heard's victims, and must not glamorize a domestic abuser. Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry. Do the right thing. Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2.

message: LA' ACUAPOLÉMICA Hace un tiempo les habíamos comentado como Amber Heard (Mera en Aquaman) había denunciado a Johnny Depp, su ex-pareja, no sólo de tratar de que Warner no le diese el papel en la película sino también de varios abusos y maltratos físicos y psicológicos durante su tiempo como pareja. Tras la denuncia y las investigaciones correspondientes, también salió a la luz de que Heard había golpeado reiteradas veces a Depp e incluso llegado a romperle un dedo con una botella de vodka, lo que llevó al actor a tener que realizarse una cirugía en la mano. Además, aparentemente surgió una noticia de que Heard había sido arrestada en 2009 también por abusos contra otra pareja. Es por eso que en estos momentos se subió un pedido a change.org ( https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2 ) (si, ya sabemos que ésta página es una de las más bastardeadas en los últimos años) para pedirle a Warner Bros y DC Entertainment que saquen a la actriz de la próxima "Aquaman 2" (16 de diciembre de 2022). La petición, que ya lleva acumulada más de 37000 firmas, toma como falsas las denuncias de Heard y la llama "la abusadora de la relación". "Amber Heard es una abusadora doméstica conocida y confirmada. DC y Warner deben eliminarla de su proyecto Aquaman 2. No se debe ignorar el sufrimiento de las víctimas y seguir dándole reconocimiento y glamour a una abusadora" reza el pedido.

description:
‼️🧜‍♀️Film News🧜‍♀️‼️

Petition will Rauswurf von Amber Heard 

Fans fordern den Rauswurf von Amber Heard aus Aquaman 2, da bei der dailymail nun eine Tonband Aufnahme aufgetaucht ist, indem die Mera Darstellerin zugibt Johnny Depp geschlagen zu haben.

Der Rosenkrieg zwischen den beiden Schauspielern dauert nun schon längere Zeit an. Depp's Verteidigung legte kürzlich neue Beweise in Form von Fotos und einer Tonbandaufnahme vor, die Beweisen sollen, dass Heard selbst Gewalt gegenüber Depp ausgeübt haben soll.
(Unter anderem soll Heard eine Zigarette auf Depp's Backe ausgedrückt und Glasflaschen nach ihm geworfen haben, wobei Depp ein Stück seines Fingers abgetrennt wurde.)

Als Amber Heard 2017 die Scheidung von Depp einreichte, behauptete Sie dass Depp Sie mehrfach misshandelt haben soll und bekam von der #metoo Bewegung deutlichen Zuspruch, der dazu geführt hat, dass Depp aus der Rolle des Captain Jack Sparrow, der Fluch der Karibik Reihe von Disney gefeuert wurde.

Auf change.org hat eine Petition gegen Heard mittlerweile über 160.000 Unterschriften gesammelt. 
Die Petition richtet sich an Senior Vice President of Publicity & Communications for DC Warner Bros Courtney Simmons und Paul McGuire, Corporate Communications of DC Entertainment.

Jetzt bleibt abzuwarten, ob die Warner Bros. Chefs sich davon beeindrucken lassen.

Was meint ihr dazu?
Findet ihr es gerechtfertigt dass Amber Heard als Mera gefeuert wird, falls die Anschuldigungen gegen Sie wahr sein sollten?

message: Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 ”Amber Heard has been exposed as a domestic abuser by Johnny Depp. In his $50 million lawsuit, Johnny Depp describes many incidents of domestic abuse that he suffered at the hands of his (then) wife Amber Heard, including one incident where she punched him twice in the face and another where she shattered his finger with a vodka bottle, and his finger had to be surgically reattached. He will bear the scar from that for the rest of his life. Also, Amber Heard was arrested in 2009 for abusing a former domestic partner, Tasya Van Ree, demonstrating a repeated pattern of abuse by Amber Heard. Since Heard's divorce from Johnny Depp, she has systematically crusaded to ruin Depp in Hollywood, repeating multiple accounts of fake incidents in which she had actually abused Johnny Depp, but lied and created false accounts of him being the abuser. About the incident during which she shattered the bones in Johnny Depp's finger and nearly severed it, causing Depp to require surgery to reattach and repair it, Heard presented a false story claiming that he cut off his finger himself, dipped it in paint and scrawled obscenities all over the walls. Likewise, Heard recounts fabricated incidents of Johnny Depp hitting her in the face when she had, in fact, punched him. Though staff and neighbors in the building where she lived reported seeing no marks on her face in the hours and days after she says Johnny Depp hit her, yet she appeared in court six (6) days later with bruises on her face, asking for a temporary restraining order, which was granted. Photos of Heard from the very next day show her full face, without makeup, and not a single bruise. As Amber Heard is a known and proven domestic abuser, Warner Brothers and DC Entertainment should and must remove Heard from their Aquaman 2 film project. They must not ignore the suffering of Heard's victims, and must not glamorize a domestic abuser. Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry. Do the right thing. Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2.“

caption: change.org
description: Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2
message: # Over 1.5M people signed a petition to remove Amber Heard from 'Aquaman 2' **Published **November 28, 2020 9:08am Over 1.5 million people have signed a petition to have Amber Heard removed from "Aquaman 2." Addressed to Warner Bros and DC Entertainment, the [Change.org](https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2) petition demanded that action "be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry." "Do the right thing," it said. "Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2." The petition was started by one Jeanne Larson, and her sentiments were echoed by 1,536,944 people as of posting. Her goal is to reach 3 million signatures. Calls for Heard's removal surfaced after her ex-husband Johnny Depp claimed that he suffered abuse from her hands, contradicting her [allegations that he was a wife beater](https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/showbiz/showbizabroad/747591/actress-amber-heard-to-be-quizzed-over-her-depp-wife-beater-claims/story/). Depp, meanwhile, was [asked to resign](https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/showbiz/showbizabroad/763125/johnny-depp-out-of-fantastic-beasts-after-losing-court-case/story/) from the cast of "Fantastic Beasts" by AT&T Inc's Warner Bros movie studio after he lost a libel case in Britain against a tabloid that called him a "wife beater." The two celebrities [finalized their tumultuous divorce](https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/showbiz/content/595761/actors-johnny-depp-amber-heard-finalize-bitter-divorce/story/) in January 2017. **—JCB, GMA News**
name: NEWSCENTER  the news that matters

Un millón de personas han firmado una petición donde exigen despedir a Amber Heard de 'Aquaman 2' después de que gracias a su acusación, se destruyera la carrera de Johnny Depp y quedará fuera de Animales Fantásticos. 

Ámber Head ganó la batalla final. 

 Johnny Depp fue obligado a abandonar la saga ‘Animales fantásticos’ tras perder el juicio con ‘The Sun’ luego de llamarle "maltratador" aunque Depp presentó bastantes pruebas de maltrato por parte de ella hacia él, entre ellas fotos en el hospital y audios donde ella era la malvada de la historia. 

Muchos aseguran que perdió el juicio y ahora es señalado en redes sociales sólo por ser hombre.

Si eres team Depp y quieres firmar la petición:

message: # **LOS FANS DE JOHNNY DEPP CONTRAATACAN CON UNA PETICIÓN PARA DESPEDIR A AMBER HEARD DE AQUAMAN 2** Amber Heard ha sido últimamente el centro de una controversia con su exmarido Johnny Depp. Depp y Heard, que se conocieron en el set de la película The Rum Diary en el 2011, y se casaron en la isla privada de Depp en las Bahamas en 2015. Después de solicitar el divorcio en 2016, Heard obtuvo una orden de restricción contra Depp, acusándolo de abusarla física y verbalmente. Todas las acusaciones preocupantes llevaron a críticas por el hecho de que Depp fuera elegido como Grindelwald en las películas de Animales Fantásticos en 2016. Depp demandó a Heard por difamación en 2019, después de que ella escribiera un artículo de opinión para The Washington Post afirmando ser víctima de violencia doméstica durante su matrimonio de corta duración. Depp también demandó a la publicación británica The Sun después de que lo llamaran un "golpeador de esposas" en uno de sus artículos. El caso fue a juicio en julio, y el lunes pasado el juez falló en contra de Depp, afirmando que él desmentía que hubiera pruebas suficientes para respaldar las afirmaciones de Heard. Poco después, Depp anunció que Warner Bros. le pidió que renunciara a su rol de Animales Fantásticos 3, y el estudio confirmó que él sería reemplazado. La decisión provocó la indignación de los fanáticos del actor, quienes lanzaron una petición en línea exigiendo que se despidiera a Heard de Aquaman 2, creyendo que Heard debería enfrentar las mismas consecuencias profesionales que Depp. La petición de Change.org titulada "***Eliminar a Amber Heard de Aquaman 2***" ha alcanzado más de ***un millón*** de firmas al cierre de ésta nota. La petición dice en parte: > *"Amber Heard ha sido expuesta como abusadora doméstica por Johnny Depp. En su demanda de $50 millones, Johnny Depp describe muchos incidentes de abuso doméstico que sufrió a manos de su (entonces) esposa Amber Heard, incluido un incidente en el que ella lo golpeó dos veces en la cara y otro en el que le rompió el dedo con una botella de vodka y su dedo tuvo que volversele a unir quirúrgicamente. Él llevará la cicatriz de eso por el resto de su vida."* Sólo el tiempo dirá si los ejecutivos de Warner Bros. o de su compañía corporativa, AT&T responden a la petición. La petición se encuentra en esta dirección: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

Un millón de personas han firmado una petición donde exigen despedir a Amber Heard de 'Aquaman 2' después de que gracias a su acusación, se destruyera la carrera de Johnny Depp y quedará fuera de Animales Fantásticos. 

Ámber Head ganó la batalla final. 

 Johnny Depp fue obligado a abandonar la saga ‘Animales fantásticos’ tras perder el juicio con ‘The Sun’ luego de llamarle "maltratador" aunque Depp presentó bastantes pruebas de maltrato por parte de ella hacia él, entre ellas fotos en el hospital y audios donde ella era la malvada de la historia. 

Muchos aseguran que perdió el juicio y ahora es señalado en redes sociales sólo por ser hombre.

เมื่อสัปดาห์ที่แล้วมีข่าวที่น่าตกใจสำหรับแฟนคลับภาพยนตร์ Fantastic Beasts เป็นอย่างมาก เมื่อทาง Warner Bros. ได้สั่งปลดป๋า Johnny Depp ออกจากบท เกลเลิร์ต กรินเดลวัลด์

เนื่องจากเขาแพ้การฟ้องร้องคดีความกับสื่อ The Sun เกี่ยวกับการพาดหัวข่าวว่าเขาเป็น "พวกตบตีภรรยา"

เรื่องนี้สร้างความไม่พอใจให้เหล่าแฟนคลับและคนที่สนับสนุนป๋า Johnny เป็นอย่างมากค่ะ

จึงทำให้ในตอนนี้เกิดการเรียกร้องให้ทาง Warner Bros. ถอด Amber Heard อดีตภรรยาของป๋าออกจากบทควีนเมรา ในภาพยนตร์ Aquaman 2 บ้าง เพราะเธอก็มีข่าวฉาวและมีหลักฐานว่าทำร้ายสามีไม่ต่างกัน

ซึ่งผู้คนพากันเรียกร้องให้ถอด Amber ออกจากบทเมราผ่านทางเว็บไซต์ Change.org โดยขณะที่กำลังเขียนข่าวนี้อยู่มีคนเข้ามาลงชื่อมากกว่า 1,127,000 คนแล้ว จากที่เมื่อวานตัวเลขอยู่ที่ 980,000 คน

ในขณะเดียวกัน ทางด้าน Amber ได้ออกมายืนยันว่าตนจะกลับมาเล่นบทบาทนี้อย่างแน่นอน ซึ่งยังไม่มีการคอนเฟิร์มจาก Warner Bros. แต่อย่างใด

เรียบเรียงโดย #ชอบดูหนัง

caption: change.org
description: Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2
message: I’ve never signed a petition like this one, but I felt moved to do so and to share. I sign thousands of political and particularly domestic animal/wildlife-related petitions every year, but, again, this is a first. And I am sharing it here not because I have been a fan of Johnny Depp for decades but because in 2015 he raised a lot of international awareness about the importance of #bats by “adopting” an orphaned bat being cared for by the Australian Bat Clinic & Wildlife Trauma Centre while he was filming in Australia. This kind of celebrity attention to the plight of bats and their vital importance to our ecosystems is priceless. This petition already has 1.5 million signatures with a goal of 3 million. I didn’t join this petition with a punitive spirit but rather to lend my support to a good man and friend to animals whom I believe is being falsely accused and who needs all the support and love he can get at this time. Thank you.
